orangelight.title: Remove "New Services" Block on Catalog Homepage
Availability not displayed for records in reserves

comments.body:
For these records we make a second call to bib data to get the availability and the result of this second call is not being handled correctly. 

This was an issue introduced when I updated the code to [handle availability for bound-with records](https://github.com/pulibrary/orangelight/pull/2553). In particular, the call to `update_single` now expects two parameters and the AJAX success method is only passing one.
